          <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Community Bank Flexibility Act </strong></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code, with respect to the tax treatment of small banks, to: (1) allow such banks to reorganize as either corporations or partnerships for tax purposes, (2) permit such banks to reorganize without incurring an additional tax for liquidation, and (3) impose a five-year recognition period of the built-in gains of such banks.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2015-07-29T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <actionDate>2015-07-29</actionDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
        </item>
